reviewText: This thing turned out to be a major disappointment. It is a series of vignettes and kind of funny. It might be an OK rental, but is definately not worth purchasing. I don't know what was banned then resurrected, but it appeared pretty tame by most softcore standards and would probably have gotten a "R" for the Nudity, if rated. I gave it two stars as I was feeling charitable. Charlie S.
British-made silly vignettes shot on 90's style video.  Not pretty people, not funny, not very sexy.
